{"tid":788460,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"淘寶集運咪用4px","createTime":"2018-08-21T13:21:36.000Z","updateTime":"2018-08-30T12:30:24.000Z","uid":93971,"like":6,"dislike":6,"uniUserReply":9,"replies":[{"pid":"a9c383be91bffa1b908f074d6f3de08a63629d1a","tid":788460,"uid":93971,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-21T13:21:36.000Z","msg":"買左千幾蚊用官方集運4px<br />\n兩個月冇到<br />\n冇物流msg<br />\n打去話兩日內覆我 呢個步驟重複左N次<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/flowerface.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n打去香港4px 話搵大陸4px 最多退2000 搵香港冇用 佢地唔個大陸咩情況 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n用online客服 頂 不停叫我搵第二個 第二個又叫我搵第三個 第三個叫我搵第一個 無限loop<br />\n最後話record左 兩日內call我again 呢個步驟重複左N次<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/flowerface.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n完全冇下文<br />\n咁就開心冇左千幾蚊<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fire.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />  <br />\n唔會再用4px <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n同啲客服chat到想隔住個mon打落去<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"991c6364b1e424e1e6bd1ca42dce130711eeaa96","tid":788460,"uid":41818,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-24T11:43:58.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/scare.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4c2c1c361d985b02377f4e57bfed3b8ecda8519e","tid":788460,"uid":160760,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-24T11:45:04.000Z","msg":"淘寶<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"44e6358847c30f5e0cfc490c6d3f65efbb22d1c4","tid":788460,"uid":170015,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-08-24T11:49:24.000Z","msg":"4px<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/no.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/no.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /